<ab facs="#facs_116_r1l15">vnd Jr in etwas <expan>Jrru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> mıt <expan>eınand<ex>er</ex></expan> ſeyt / von <expan>etlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſprechnüſſ</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
